data.description: Fully REMODELED TOWNHOUSE. ALL AGES welcome in this gorgeous community. This charming 2 bed/2 bath situated on a desirable corner lot, radiates warmth & style. Inside, a calming color scheme compliments the wood-look flooring throughout, leading into a cozy living room. The kitchen impresses with white cabinetry, sleek built-in appliances with a BRAND NEW SS refrigerator,  polished countertops, recessed lighting & ample storage. The main bedroom features a private exit & an ensuite, both bedrooms offering HUGE walk-in closets. A rare floorplan for this neighborhood. Outside, the backyard is a private oasis with a covered patio, paver seating area & low-maintenance artificial turf. Additional perks include a 2-car detached garage & access to the community pool. A must-see property-MUST SEE
